Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.02,0:23:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的“萌”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.86,0:23:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，对了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近好像也有人称这个为“哈…哈”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.26,0:23:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的辛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.66,0:23:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样
